<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> 9. Is Rathe so an@l retentive that we tell clerics &quot;don't do your epic cause your not ALLOWED to get it until lvl 56, because RTA says so?&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
